8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High server_error_ratio and error_ratio as well as rrt_max observed during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics show server_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 0.33 and error_ratio from 0.0 to 0.33. Max response time (rrt_max) soared from 230156 to 20054398.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Severe increase in response times (rrt and rrt_max) during the anomaly.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics indicate rrt increased from 7666.71 to 1200155.01 and rrt_max from 209404 to 20064612.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client error ratio spiked dramatically during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Client error ratio escalated from 0.0 to 43.64 in 99th percentile values.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "### 错误日志分析结果\n\n在分析来自UUID `9b0004fb-390`的错误日志后，以下是显著的异常调用链和关键词：\n\n**识别的异常模式**\n\n1. **错误类型**:\n   - `rpc error: code = Unavailable`\n   - `timed out waiting for server handshake`\n   - `transport: Error while dialing`\n   - `i/o timeout`\n   - `connection error`\n\n2. **日志标签**:\n   - `shipping quote failure`\n\n**分析出的公共嫌疑服务**\n\n从日志中可以看到，所有错误日志均来自 `frontend` 服务，而这些错误都与其与其他服务（可能是 `shipping` 服务）之间的 RPC 调用失败有关。\n\n**故障模式**\n\n通过分析订单完成时的RPC调用失败，结合关键词 `timed out waiting for server handshake` 和 `i/o timeout`，可以判断出问题可能与网络通信延迟或服务连接问题有关。\n\n**DNS 故障**\n\n- 没有发现 DNS 相关的错误。\n\n**Port Misconfiguration**\n\n- 没有发现端口配置错误相关的日志，所有错误均与 `shipping quote` RPC调用有关。\n\n### JSON输出结果\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"rpc error: code = Unavailable\",\n    \"timed out waiting for server handshake\",\n    \"transport: Error while dialing\",\n    \"i/o timeout\",\n    \"connection error\",\n    \"shipping quote failure\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection timeout issues during shipping quote retrieval\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"network communication error during order processing\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 结论\n\n从日志分析可以看到，`frontend` 服务遇到RPC调用失败的问题导致订单无法完成。这可能与网络通信问题有关，具体原因可能是服务之间的连接超时或网络拥堵现象。进一步调查服务之间的网络状况及配置可能提供更多线索。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据trace数据分析，以下是显著的异常调用链和可能的根因：\n\n### 异常发现\n- 延迟倍数计算和根因识别：\n  - `checkoutservice->shippingservice`: 正常平均耗时为 9415.74 ms，异常平均耗时为 19587979.70 ms，延迟倍数为 2079.9。显然存在严重延迟。\n  - `frontend->checkoutservice`: 正常平均耗时约为 150000 ms，异常时段超过 20000000 ms，主要是由于调用 `shippingservice` 时的延迟。\n  - `checkoutservice->productcatalogservice`: 正常平均耗时为 10774.14 ms，异常平均耗时为 17421.25 ms，延迟倍数为 1.62，可能也与整体延迟上升有关。\n\n### 错误状态分析\n- 连接错误情况频繁出现：\n  - `checkoutservice->shippingservice` 出现大量连接超时 (`connection error`)：频次85次，通常与无法与服务器建立连接或响应过慢有关。\n  - 多个调用链中存在 `Unavailable` 错误，进一步证实 `shippingservice` 可能是根因。\n\n### 关键调用链标识\n- Detected Trace Keys:\n  - **延迟指标**: `rrt_max`\n  - **错误状态**: `error_ratio`\n  - **调用关系**: `checkoutservice->shippingservice`\n\n### 结论\n从trace数据中可以看出，`shippingservice`的异常操作以及延迟是此次故障的根因。由于该服务的超时和断开连接导致了严重的调用链延迟，特别是在`CheckoutService/PlaceOrder`过程中的表现最明显。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段平均耗时为19587979.70 ms，与正常耗时相比有显著延迟倍数。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"大量连接超时错误，使得无法与服务建立正常连接。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
